front.title: SFS L-s7.2 TIE Cannon
front.gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on any TIE (for free if a TIE/ln). May target a starship using 1 Force. Draw Destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value.
front.lore: TIE cannon mass produced at Wakeelmui system. Campatable with multiple TIE models for ease of deployment.
